This quest, much like many others in the game, was poorly thought out in my opinion.  Any quest item required by one class, but made desirable by several, doesn't seem too smart.  The fix for this one is extremely simple, but as long as we all pay our monthly fees it, like all the rest, will never be corrected.  I think they should either not require mages to get this item to gain thier epic,or fix it as follows.<br>
<br>
1)  Make it mage only-This is an outstanding item.  Any kind of lev is great for a melee at any level and a free lev is also nice for lazy casters, myself included.<br>
<br>
2) Make it non MQable-This requires the mage to work for it themselves as well as not allowing Greedybastard_01 to bend you over and give you a good 40K screwing.<br>
<br>
Ok, bitch at me now and tell me how wrong I am.<br>
